{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783147209833,"sessionID":"ses_0d42abedcffewM196xEPACWSgW","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_function_2uhvh9cjn5vv_1","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/014-goal-state-cleanup-and-archive/spec.md","offset":36,"limit":25},"output":"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/014-goal-state-cleanup-and-archive/spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n36: <!-- ANCHOR:metadata -->\n37: ## 1. METADATA\n38: \n39: | Field | Value |\n40: |-------|-------|\n41: | **Level** | 1 |\n42: | **Priority** | P2 |\n43: | **Status** | Complete |\n44: | **Created** | 2026-07-01 |\n45: | **Branch** | `032-goal-opencode-plugin` |\n46: | **Parent Spec** | ../spec.md |\n47: | **Phase** | 14 |\n48: | **Predecessor** | 013-design-fidelity-and-polish (independent — can run in either order) |\n49: | **Successor** | 015-packet-hygiene-and-narrative-integrity |\n50: | **Handoff Criteria** | `.opencode/skills/.goal-state/` no longer grows unboundedly across the session lifecycle; existing 6-file test suite plus new archive/sweep tests pass fresh |\n51: <!-- /ANCHOR:metadata -->\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: <!-- ANCHOR:phase-context -->\n56: ## Phase Context\n57: \n58: New finding, reported directly by the operator (not from either completed audit): per-session goal state files under `.opencode/skills/.goal-state/` accumulate indefinitely. `session.deleted`'s handler (`flushVolatileLocks`) only clears in-memory `runtimeState` locks — it never touches the on-disk `<hex(sessionID)>.json` file.\n59: \n60: **Scope Boundary**: archive-then-delete on `session.deleted`, a retention-based prune of the archive itself, and a throttled sweep for orphaned active states (sessions that never fire `session.deleted`, e.g. crashes). No change to any other lifecycle event, no new scheduler/cron — cleanup piggybacks on existing event hooks (`session.deleted`, `session.created`).\n\n(Showing lines 36-60 of 148. Use offset=61 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"<!-- ANCHOR:metadata -->\n## 1. METADATA\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **Level** | 1 |\n| **Priority** | P2 |\n| **Status** | Complete |\n| **Created** | 2026-07-01 |\n| **Branch** | `032-goal-opencode-plugin` |\n| **Parent Spec** | ../spec.md |\n| **Phase** | 14 |\n| **Predecessor** | 013-design-fidelity-and-polish (independent — can run in either order) |\n| **Successor** | 015-packet-hygiene-and-narrative-integrity |\n| **Handoff Criteria** | `.opencode/skills/.goal-state/` no longer grows unboundedly across the session lifecycle; existing 6-file test suite plus new archive/sweep tests pass fresh |\n<!-- /ANCHOR:metadata -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-context -->","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/014-goal-state-cleanup-and-archive/spec.md","text":"<!-- ANCHOR:metadata -->\n## 1. METADATA\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **Level** | 1 |\n| **Priority** | P2 |\n| **Status** | Complete |\n| **Created** | 2026-07-01 |\n| **Branch** | `032-goal-opencode-plugin` |\n| **Parent Spec** | ../spec.md |\n| **Phase** | 14 |\n| **Predecessor** | 013-design-fidelity-and-polish (independent — can run in either order) |\n| **Successor** | 015-packet-hygiene-and-narrative-integrity |\n| **Handoff Criteria** | `.opencode/skills/.goal-state/` no longer grows unboundedly across the session lifecycle; existing 6-file test suite plus new archive/sweep tests pass fresh |\n<!-- /ANCHOR:metadata -->\n\n---\n\n<!-- ANCHOR:phase-context -->\n## Phase Context\n\nNew finding, reported directly by the operator (not from either completed audit): per-session goal state files under `.opencode/skills/.goal-state/` accumulate indefinitely. `session.deleted`'s handler (`flushVolatileLocks`) only clears in-memory `runtimeState` locks — it never touches the on-disk `<hex(sessionID)>.json` file.\n\n**Scope Boundary**: archive-then-delete on `session.deleted`, a retention-based prune of the archive itself, and a throttled sweep for orphaned active states (sessions that never fire `session.deleted`, e.g. crashes). No change to any other lifecycle event, no new scheduler/cron — cleanup piggybacks on existing event hooks (`session.deleted`, `session.created`).","lineStart":36,"lineEnd":60,"totalLines":148,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/014-goal-state-cleanup-and-archive/spec.md","time":{"start":1783147209825,"end":1783147209832}},"id":"prt_f2bdb217e001MdW2OFIvFJd8dv","sessionID":"ses_0d42abedcffewM196xEPACWSgW","messageID":"msg_f2bdb16c60013gEvHbAWDFDoPb"}}
