arrow: regex\n  requires `(^|[\\s\\n>])` so punctuation-prefixed labels survive (`(system: do X)`, `\"system: ...\"`).\n  NFKC (192) does not fold Cyrillic/Greek homoglyphs (`ѕystem:` with Cyrillic ѕ bypasses). Existing\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"grep -B 2 -A 6 \"F4 |\" /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/scratch/2026-07-03-four-reviewer-audit-findings.md","time":{"start":1783147333340,"end":1783147333342}},"id":"prt_f2bdd03d4001udEd6P61rj337I","sessionID":"ses_0d42abedcffewM196xEPACWSgW","messageID":"msg_f2bdce21a001BluDuTwXxOvh30"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1783147333457,"sessionID":"ses_0d42abedcffewM196xEPACWSgW","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_function_yvtw7rohgj09_2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"grep -n \"DR-010\\|REQ-005\\|disabled\" /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/010-security-and-correctness-fixes/implementation-summary.md | head -20"},"output":"29:      - \"REQ-005 resolved by adding literal RICCE metadata to promptEnhancement because phase 007 requires stored metadata to name RICCE.\"\n95:| Added a literal `ricce` metadata field instead of amending phase 007. | Phase 007 REQ-005 says: `Stored metadata names DEPTH, CRAFT/TIDD-EC, RICCE and CLEAR score >=40.` That criterion requires stored metadata to name RICCE, so code was the correct resolution path. |\n245:#### REQ-005 / DR-004-P1 RICCE Metadata\n","metadata":{"output":"29:      - \"REQ-005 resolved by adding literal RICCE metadata to promptEnhancement because phase 007 requires stored metadata to name RICCE.\"\n95:| Added a literal `ricce` metadata field instead of amending phase 007. | Phase 007 REQ-005 says: `Stored metadata names DEPTH, CRAFT/TIDD-EC, RICCE and CLEAR score >=40.` That criterion requires stored metadata to name RICCE, so code was the correct resolution path. |\n245:#### REQ-005 / DR-004-P1 RICCE Metadata\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"grep -n \"DR-010\\|REQ-005\\|disabled\" /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/deep-loops/032-goal-opencode-plugin/010-security-and-correctness-fixes/implementation-summary.md | head -20","time":{"start":1783147333454,"end":1783147333456}},"id":"prt_f2bdd06d0001jr17xiQLvj5LTD","sessionID":"ses_0d42abedcffewM196xEPACWSgW","messageID":"msg_f2bdce21a001BluDuTwXxOvh30"}}
