tinuation Mode Evidence\n### Regression Anchor Evidence\n## 8. PASS/FAIL\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"wc -l /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/manual_testing_playbook/02--cli-hooks-and-plugin/goal-opencode-plugin.md\necho \"---\"\n# Check the rest of the playbook\ngrep -E \"^##\" /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/manual_testing_playbook/02--cli-hooks-and-plugin/goal-opencode-plugin.md | head -20","time":{"start":1783147923895,"end":1783147923897}},"id":"prt_f2be6047d001mCALwfsCEEob1b","sessionID":"ses_0d42abedcffewM196xEPACWSgW","messageID":"msg_f2be5f02b001T3wJxrmmVK1Vwv"}}
